SUMMARY:StarLab Mobile Planetarium
DESCRIPTION:Join us June 15-29th to visit the StarLab Mobile Planetarium. Multiple showtimes each day! \nThe IU13 StarLab Mobile Planetarium lets you explore the galaxy and learn about the solar system up close\, right from The Lancaster Science Factory. Learn the names of constellations and how they tell stories about different cultures around the world. \nThere are multiple showtimes each day. This event is presented free with admission.
URL:https://lancastersciencefactory.org/event/starlabplanetarium/2026-06-27/
LOCATION:The Lancaster Science Factory\, 454 New Holland Ave\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
